Horror from 2006 by Harry Basil with Leah Pipes and Kristin Cavallari.


The story

Based on an actual small town legend, "Fingerprints" is a supernatural thriller, where a trip down haunted railroad tracks includes a stop at a railroad crossing, where fifty years earlier a train crashed into a school bus, killing most of the town?s children. The ghosts of this horrific disaster beckon to Melanie and lead the troubled teen to discover the horrifying truth hidden in a destination not on any map.
